{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_12_02",
  "title": "白石沙季",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "沙季……大丈夫か？\n一体何があったんだ？",
      "startTime": 2.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 0.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.6590249221
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\n私、監督の要望にうまく沿うことが出来なくて……",
      "startTime": 6.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "「一度休んで気持ちを入れ替えておいで」と\n気まで遣わせてしまいました……",
      "startTime": 15.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.3194105625
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そんな……沙季はあんなに準備してきたじゃないか\n監督はどんな要望を出してきたんだ？",
      "startTime": 22.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "それが、切ない映像に加えて、明るい映像……\n思いっきりはしゃいでいる姿も撮りたい、と",
      "startTime": 30.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.1931739648
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なんだって？\nそれじゃあ曲のテーマと真逆じゃないか",
      "startTime": 35.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "はい……『君の残り香』は夏らしさはありますが\n夏の終わりを感じさせる、切ないテーマの楽曲です",
      "startTime": 44.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.7155783177
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "あの切なさや儚さを表現するために、いろんな\nアイドルの写真集や、MVを見て勉強してきました",
      "startTime": 52.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、逆にそのせいで、監督の目指すイメージを\nうまく表現出来なくなってしまって",
      "startTime": 61.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.3531965098
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "監督は、曲がノスタルジックだからこそ\n目一杯はしゃぐ映像がほしかったそうなんです……",
      "startTime": 67.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.1931906861
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、あえて曲とは真逆の印象を加えることで\n曲のイメージをより強くしようとしているのか……",
      "startTime": 75.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "その狙いは私も理解出来ました。ですが……\nどうすれば、はしゃいで見えるのかが分からなくて……",
      "startTime": 84.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.5928094071
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "はしゃぐ、か。確かに沙季は知的なイメージだし\nそういうことを求められるのは初めてかもな",
      "startTime": 93.6666712443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "実は、監督に「芽衣ちゃんみたいな感じで」と\n助け舟を出していただけたので、その……",
      "startTime": 101.2000045776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.5561463199
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "み、みんなー！　沙季だよー！　えーっと、あ！\nせっかくだしプールへ飛び込もーう！　ざぶーん！",
      "startTime": 112.0333379109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.7561459385
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "といった感じで、芽衣ちゃんの真似をしながら\n飛び込んだりもしたのですが、それも撮り直しに……",
      "startTime": 120.7666712443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "か、空回ってしまったんだな……\n無理にはしゃいでもぎこちなくなるだけだもんな……",
      "startTime": 128.3333379109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.5830137734
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "はしゃぐって、本当になんなんでしょうか……\n何をすれば、はしゃいでいるのを表現出来るんでしょう",
      "startTime": 135.5000045776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.5948650205
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "苦戦するのは仕方ないさ。普段と違うキャラを\n演じるのは、どんな人だって即興では難しいはずだ",
      "startTime": 142.7666712443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "無理はしなくていい。沙季の魅力を引き出せる\n別の方向性で撮影出来ないか、交渉して――",
      "startTime": 149.7000045776,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10533.333333299994,
          "startTime": 160.2333379109
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.8699289168
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "い、いえ、大丈夫です！　今、はしゃぐ方法を\n心強い方に教わっていたところだったんですよ",
      "startTime": 157.7000045776,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6200.6227646000125,
          "startTime": 163.9006273422
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.0666712443
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ちょうど返信が来ました。ふむふむ……\nなるほど……これなら、はしゃいで見えるかも……！",
      "startTime": 167.1000178019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 167.1000178019
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.030093305
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "凄いな、既に対策を講じていたのか\nしかし……心強い方か。一応、誰か聞いてもいいか？",
      "startTime": 175.6333379109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "こころちゃんです。可愛くはしゃぐイメージは\nこころちゃんにぴったりですから",
      "startTime": 185.6333379109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 187.7455379969
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こころか……確かにぴったりだと思うが\n一応、何を教わったのかも教えてくれないか？",
      "startTime": 193.0000045776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 197.0535197104
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "実際にやってみますね。えーっと、この角度で……\n目線をカメラに……ハートを打ち抜くように……？",
      "startTime": 202.7333379109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 207.8000045776
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こほん、ではいきますよー\nはっぴーぴかぴか、す、すまいる～……えへ……",
      "startTime": 212.2666692097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 212.2666692097
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 219.0319532876
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_02-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "う、うぅ～～～～……は、恥ずかしい……\nき、聞かせて下さい……私、はしゃげてましたか？",
      "startTime": 223.8333379109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
